法規內容.條文內容:
Nomination for the NCA is held annually. The Ministry of Culture selects up to five potential NCA recipients. The list of recipients shall be approved by the Premier.
The following may nominate candidates by writing the candidate’s name and achievements:
1. NCA jury members;
2. Heads of cultural/academic organizations;
3. Heads of arts and cultural departments or institutes at universities; and
4. The responsible person of legally registered foundations or associations for the promotion of arts and culture.
